Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.29,0:18:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,就像那个在地铁里被大毛虫吃掉的杰瑞\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Like that giant caterpillar what ate Jared from subway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.92,0:18:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们这些网虫又有了新的热门视频\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Nows us Internet geeks gots a whole new video sensation.
