Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.95,0:19:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不过管它呢\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}but whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我为我的所作所为感到非常抱歉\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I am so, so sorry for what I did,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.16,0:19:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我永远无法弥补你\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}and I know I can never make it up to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你不必道歉\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}You don't have to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我是来谢谢你\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}In fact, I came to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.98,0:19:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你要打我\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}I think you mean hit me.
