Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.78,0:19:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你在新泽西周围晃荡过吗\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Were you rolling around in New Jersey?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.69,0:19:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,丽拉 我知道我没法补偿你\N{\fs14\1c&0xFFFFFF}Leela, I knew I could never make it up to you,
